PN,44601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774472757
OL,3,COfficer 'fast-forwarded' Noah CCTV
OL,4,Cfootage of missing teen twice
OL,6,FA PSNI officer has admitted to missing
OL,7,FNoah Donohoe on two CCTV cameras he is
OL,8,Fnow known to have travelled past
OL,9,Fadmitting he didn't pay the greatest
OL,10,Flevel of attention to it that he could
OL,11,Fhave.
OL,13,FIn the ninth week of the inquest into
OL,14,FNoah's death, jurors at Belfast
OL,15,Fcoroner's court heard that an officer
OL,16,Fconducting initial searches on CCTV
OL,17,F"fast-forwarded" footage on some
OL,18,Fcameras.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774472757
OL,3,COfficer 'fast-forwarded' Noah CCTV
OL,4,Cfootage of missing teen twice
OL,6,FThe court was told of how there was a
OL,7,Ftiming discrepancy between the footage
OL,8,Fand real time.
OL,10,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,11,Fwas 14 when his naked body was found
OL,12,Fin a storm drain tunnel in north
OL,13,FBelfast in June 2020, six days after
OL,14,Fhe left home on his bike to meet two
OL,15,Ffriends in the Cavehill area of the
OL,16,Fcity.
OL,18,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,19,Fcause of death was likely to be
OL,20,Fdrowning.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774472757
OL,3,COfficer 'fast-forwarded' Noah CCTV
OL,4,Cfootage of missing teen twice
OL,6,FIn early February, a PSNI detective
OL,7,Fconstable gave evidence to the inquest
OL,8,Fwhen CCTV footage was played from the
OL,9,FGrove Leisure centre, which Brenda
OL,10,FCampbell KC representing Fiona
OL,11,FDonohoe, said Noah appeared on.
OL,13,FThe constable said she had no dealings
OL,14,Fwith checking CCTV footage on Monday
OL,15,F22 June and so could not comment on
OL,16,Fwhat other officers checked or what
OL,17,Finquiries they made.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774472757
OL,3,COfficer 'fast-forwarded' Noah CCTV
OL,4,Cfootage of missing teen twice
OL,6,FAnother PSNI constable, who was
OL,7,Finvolved in searching for CCTV for
OL,8,Fseveral hours that Monday, told the
OL,9,Finquest on Wednesday he was briefed
OL,10,Fthat morning before going to the CCTV
OL,11,Foperating suite and then checking a
OL,12,Fnumber of locations.
OL,14,FHis notebook showed he visited a shop
OL,15,Fon the Ormeau Road and on North Queen
OL,16,FStreet and got positive sightings of
OL,17,FNoah on CCTV.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774472757
OL,3,COfficer 'fast-forwarded' Noah CCTV
OL,4,Cfootage of missing teen twice
OL,6,FHe later worked towards the Grove
OL,7,FLeisure Centre and Melville Morgan
OL,8,FFuneral directors, both situated on
OL,9,Fthe York Road in north Belfast, around
OL,10,Fhalf a mile from the culvert where
OL,11,FNoah's body was later found on 27 June.
OL,13,FNick Scott, acting counsel for the
OL,14,Fcoroner, showed a police log
OL,15,Fhighlighting an entry claiming CCTV
OL,16,Fwas checked at the leisure centre and
OL,17,Fthe funeral directors facing it, with
OL,18,F"negative results".
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774472757
OL,3,COfficer 'fast-forwarded' Noah CCTV
OL,4,Cfootage of missing teen twice
OL,6,FThe officer said that meant "that I
OL,7,Fdidn't view the missing person on any
OL,8,Ffootage that I viewed", adding that
OL,9,Fpolice "were just trying to plot the
OL,10,Fcourse" to track Noah's journey at
OL,11,Fthat stage.
OL,13,FAsked about his investigations at the
OL,14,FGrove, Mr Day said "the footage I
OL,15,Fviewed was what I thought was the
OL,16,Fright time for Noah going past" and
OL,17,Fthat was based "on the operator
OL,18,Fshowing me the correct footage and
OL,19,Fcorrect timings."
OL,26,@nD@]OUpD@VO]qD@HOUrD@GO]vD@TOUxD@_O]yD@
OL,26,APOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774472757
OL,3,COfficer 'fast-forwarded' Noah CCTV
OL,4,Cfootage of missing teen twice
OL,6,FOn the day he was searching CCTV for
OL,7,FNoah, the constable arrived at the
OL,8,FYork Road area at approximately 12pm
OL,9,Fbefore being redeployed on a separate
OL,10,Femergency call at 12.38pm.
OL,12,FHe agreed with Ms Campbell's
OL,13,Fassessment that he was "working with a
OL,14,F35-minute window" to get himself and a
OL,15,Fcolleague from one end of the street
OL,16,Fto the other, checking CCTV at the
OL,17,Fleisure centre and funeral directors.
OL,19,FMs Campbell said it "appears you
OL,20,Fmissed him on both sets of footage"
OL,21,Fand he replied "yes".
OL,26,@uD@XOUvD@QO]{D@UOU|D@cO]}D@POU}D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774472757
OL,3,COfficer 'fast-forwarded' Noah CCTV
OL,4,Cfootage of missing teen twice
OL,6,FThe officer agreed that he knows how
OL,7,Fto check real time versus camera time
OL,8,Fbecause he recorded doing so when
OL,9,Fretrieving CCTV from two locations
OL,10,Fearlier in the day.
OL,12,FHe further agreed that an "obvious
OL,13,Fquestion" is how far out of real time
OL,14,Fthe camera is and that is of
OL,15,Fparticular interest to the police.
OL,17,FAsked by Ms Campbell if it is
OL,18,F"fundamental policing" to check the
OL,19,Ftime difference he said "yes".
OL,26,@tD@[OUuD@IO]zD@AOUzD@VO]{D@YOU{D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774472757
OL,3,COfficer 'fast-forwarded' Noah CCTV
OL,4,Cfootage of missing teen twice
OL,6,FShe put it to the officer that there
OL,7,Fwas a high risk missing child and the
OL,8,Fpolice should have been taking "all
OL,9,Fpositive action" to which he agreed.
OL,11,FHe had previously said he watched 10
OL,12,Fminutes either side of the time he
OL,13,Fsaid he wanted to view, which in this
OL,14,Fcase was around 6pm on the night Noah
OL,15,Fwent missing.
OL,26,@pD@`OUqD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774472757
OL,3,COfficer 'fast-forwarded' Noah CCTV
OL,4,Cfootage of missing teen twice
OL,6,FWhen Ms Campbell suggested he could
OL,7,Fnot have done that in the 35-minute
OL,8,Fwindow viewing CCTV at two locations,
OL,9,Fhe said the footage "was fast-
OL,10,Fforwarded, we could have watched it
OL,11,Ffaster".
OL,13,FWhen Ms Donohoe's counsel contended
OL,14,Fthat showed the officer was "not
OL,15,Fpaying it the greatest level of
OL,16,Fattention", the officer replied, "no".
OL,26,@qD@UOUsD@GO]vD@]OUxD@JO]xD@bOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774472757
OL,3,COfficer 'fast-forwarded' Noah CCTV
OL,4,Cfootage of missing teen twice
OL,6,FMs Campbell said it was not the fault
OL,7,Fof the constable that these searches
OL,8,Fwere occurring at 12.30pm on Monday
OL,9,Fand in her team's perspective "ought
OL,10,Fto have been significantly before
OL,11,Fthat".
OL,13,FLater Mr Day agreed with Donal Lunny
OL,14,FKC, representing the PSNI, when asked
OL,15,Fif he was alive to the issue that CCTV
OL,16,Fcameras can be out of synchronisation
OL,17,Fwith real time.
OL,26,@qD@_OUsD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774472757
OL,3,COfficer 'fast-forwarded' Noah CCTV
OL,4,Cfootage of missing teen twice
OL,6,FMr Day also agreed that he believed
OL,7,Fthe time on the CCTV at the leisure
OL,8,Fcentre and funeral directors was
OL,9,Fcorrect as he watched it, and when it
OL,10,Fwas "fast-forwarded" he was "still
OL,11,Fviewing what's on the screen".
OL,13,FHe further conceded that he was not in
OL,14,Fa rush to get away and was not aware
OL,15,Fhe was going to get called away on an
OL,16,Femergency.
OL,26,@rD@EOUrD@TO]rD@]OUsD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774472757
OL,3,COfficer 'fast-forwarded' Noah CCTV
OL,4,Cfootage of missing teen twice
OL,6,FMr Lunny also highlighted in police
OL,7,Flogs that another team visited the
OL,8,Flocations on the York Road later in
OL,9,Fthe day and also experienced issues
OL,10,Fwith the quality and time-checking of
OL,11,FCCTV.
OL,13,FMs Campbell earlier brought up the log
OL,14,Ffor the PSNI's CCTV suite where the
OL,15,Fofficer is shown to have arrived at
OL,16,F9.51am on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774472757
OL,3,COfficer 'fast-forwarded' Noah CCTV
OL,4,Cfootage of missing teen twice
OL,6,FShe contested that he would appear to
OL,7,Fbe the first officer to attend the
OL,8,Fsuite in relation to Noah's
OL,9,Finvestigation, 12 hours after he had
OL,10,Fbeen reported missing, to which the
OL,11,Fconstable replied "yes".
OL,13,FMr Lunny highlighted in his
OL,14,Fquestioning there are "many ways"
OL,15,Fpolice can communicate with the CCTV
OL,16,Fcentre beyond going there in person.
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,19,FITVX
